  schema={JSON.stringify(schema)}
  canonical="https://papyruspeople.photonbuilder.com/writing-prompts-guide"
>
  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>200 Writing Prompts Guide</h1>
      <p>Ignite your creativity with our ultimate collection of writing prompts. Whether you write fiction, non-fiction, poetry, or simply want to journal, we have something to get your words flowing.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section card">
      <h2>Tips for Writers</h2>

      <h3>Overcoming Writer's Block</h3>
      <p>Writer's block can happen to anyone. To beat it, try stepping away from your desk, going for a walk, or doing a different creative activity. Sometimes, lowering your expectations and giving yourself permission to write "badly" is exactly what you need to get started again.</p>

      <h3>Building a Daily Writing Habit</h3>
      <p>Consistency is key to becoming a better writer. Set a specific time each day dedicated solely to writing. Start small, perhaps 15 minutes a day, and gradually increase. Protect this time and make it a non-negotiable part of your routine.</p>

      <h3>The Prompt-to-Story Method</h3>
      <p>When using a writing prompt, don't just answer it literally. Use it as a springboard. Ask yourself "What if?" and "Why?" about the prompt's scenario. Introduce a character with a strong desire and place an obstacle in their way based on the prompt's premise.</p>
